text.tspan: During the ascent, rocket use all of its engine
second stage keeps its way to orbit
Cold gas thrusters flip rocket’s first stage
in order to start recovery operation
Engines light to bring first stage back
First stage fly back in atmosphere while
engines light again to slow down
Grid fins steer lift produced by first stage
Payload, as weel as crew capsule, separate
from second stage and fly to final destination
